Let a = 1 -> khai bao bien a va gan gia tri 1 cho bien a

a = 2 -> cap nhat gia tri 2 cho bien "a"

Data type
number
    - int: 1, 2, 3
    - float: 1.2, 1.3
bool
    is/are/have/has + adj/N
    exp
        - isNumber = true/false
-- char
    -- exp: "a", "b"
string
    exp: "ok anh em"
object
    - array [matrix]
        exp:
            [1, 2, 3]
            [
                [1, 2, 3],
                [3, 2, 1]
            ]
    - dictionary (key - value)
        exp:
            {
                "hello": "xin chao",
                "ok": duoc
            }

Date object
Undefined
Null

Ep kieu du lieu - Convert data type

const a = 1000
convert
    1000 -> "1000" -> ok
    "1000" -> 1000 -> ok

trong toan logic:
    - chi co true or false
    - sai: false -> 0
    - dung: true (khong phai false) -> khong phai 0
    - sai: false -> ""


 number          string         bool          status

  1000 ────────► "1000"                          o
  1000 ◄──────── "1000"                          o
                 "true" ◄────── true             o
                 "true" ──────► true            o x
   1   ◄─────────────────────── true             ?
  1000 ────────────────────────►true             o


